title: Congrats To Tom DeLonge On His UFO Researcher Of The Year Award
text: Two years ago, under contentious circumstances , Blink-182 co-founder Tom DeLonge was kicked out of the band. Since then, he's had time to pursue other interests. Like: UFO research! DeLonge, who claims that he's had contact with aliens , was one of the people whose emails with Hillary Clinton consigliere John Podesta leaked … More »
